    section#about.container
      .row
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2 
          h2.section-heading about              
          p
            | By college students, for college students. 
          p
            | We wanted to communicate comfortably and conveniently with other college students around us, but there was nothing out there, so we created it. We hope you find this as helpful as we have; its made our college experience that much better. #whateveryoudo #dontgraduate
          p
            | Start and pop conversations with only students around you. It’s local communication done right. 
          p(style='font-size:20pt')
            | Be 
            b anonymous
            |, or just be 
            b you
            | . Anywhere. Anytime.
          p 
            | Set your distance. Reach who you want to reach. It’s your community, and it’s your content. spop provides the platform for you to make your college experience that much better.
          p
            span(style='font-size:20pt') Nothing 
            |is permanent. Why should your conversations be? spops pop when you leave. Or you can pop them yourself. Once they've 
            span(style='font-size:20pt') popped
